          Therefore many patients may have a history of nail damage through playing sports or use of gel nails and pedicures.
          In some cases there is a strong family history of nail problems too. Over the counter products are not always effective
          for everybody. Podiatrist can offer comprehensive treatment and management of the condition. Feet Foremost provide
          a range of
          <b> fungal treatments and management options to eradicate the infection and improve the appearance of effected nails.
