          formulate a treatment plan. The plan may involve exercises or modifying your exercise or sporting regime as well
          as devices to support or stretch structures during activity. We may also issue prescription orthotic devises which
          can help realign the body during posture and activity. Unlike ‘off the shelf’ high street products,
